We may also share your name and phone number with your local healthcare authorities to help them track cases.

profile__diagnosed__message__yes:
By pressing the button below, all contacts you've met in the last two weeks will be notified that they might have come in contact with someone who is now diagnosed with Coronavirus.

This is so they can get tested and keep themselves safe. Don't be alarmed, we won't reveal your identity to your contacts.

We may also share your name and phone number with your local healthcare authorities to help them track cases.

Please confirm that you are positive for COVID-19.

profile__tracking__message:
This feature tracks your location at all times. This data can be useful for healthcare professionals to track cases of COVID-19 even if you forget to log your meetings or visits.

Sharing this data with us is completely optional. We understand that this is very sensitive and we go to great lengths to protect your data.
